Media Personality, Toke Makinwa, 35, has flagged off a search for Christmas romance with anyone that will make her feel good. Toke Makinwa stated that the romance will only last for only two weeks as they will break up after the yuletide. She however added that she’s got expensive taste. She tweeted: “Looking for Christmas romance only for 2 weeks, someone that’ll spin me make my belle sweet. We break up after the yuletide season, any takers? In short 2, one is too small, I need a romance for 2 weeks, I’ve got expensive taste so come correct o, merry soon Christmas” Source